Tool-aware narration preview cadence lifecycle.

start:
- When tool-aware queue is in tool_active and receives buffered narration deltas.
- Begin periodic preview emission at the configured cadence.

stop:
- On tool_end, error, done, text_final, or dispose.
- Clear preview cadence timers to avoid post-run emissions.

Safety boundary:
- Preview narration is display-only and must not be used as canonical action-parse input.
